Explanation:
The first operation swaps the first two elements of the array (A0A_0A0​ and A1A_1A1​), so the array becomes {2,3,1}\{2, 3, 1\}{2,3,1}
The second operation swaps the second and third elements of the array, so the array becomes {2,1,3}\{2, 1, 3\}{2,1,3}
The third operation swaps the first two elements of the array, so the array becomes {1,2,3}\{1, 2, 3\}{1,2,3}
You can verify that it cannot be done in less than 333 operations.
